# Li Studio demo — native only

World Studio’s shipped runtime is **native Li** (`li-studio`, `li-ui`, `li-gui`, `li-render`, `li-sim-*`) and native hosts.

## Allowed

- Native composition + paint in `li-studio` / `li-ui` / `li-gui`
- Li rasterizer pixels presented via SDL/host; `li-render` / `lig` viewport paths
- MCP dispatch through `studio_mcp_tool_*`
- Smokes under `li-tests/smoke/` and `packages/*/li-tests/smoke/`

## Forbidden

- Treating `deploy/studio-demo/*.html` (marketing mocks) as the shipped app/runtime
- Using HTML/CSS/JS studio runtime as product proof

## Proof requirement

When claiming progress/completion, provide native artifacts:

- `docs/demo/media/native-verticals/png/*.png` screenshots from native pixels
- `lic check` / `lic build` gates where required by the current plan loop
